{"tid":734867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查發現九成劏房戶被濫收水電費","createTime":"2018-07-09T04:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T16:45:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b921930e74f4841d53b5419773d5a7f690c1166","tid":734867,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"兩電加電費令基層市民百上加斤，劏房戶更長期被業主濫收水電費。港大進行調查發現逾九成住戶被業主多收水電費用，被收取的水費及電費平均是一般收費的2.2倍及1.4倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，港大指曾有住戶嘗試透過小額錢債審裁處追討多收費用，惟因欠缺租約等原因難以追討<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，批評政府至今拒監管劏房是失職<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180709/large/0708wai1010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180709%2Flarge%2F0708wai1010.jpg&h=40ae7859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">■ 劏房戶陳太指每月水電費達400多元，其租約列明的水電費平均較一般高。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180709/20444738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F20444738&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=484c24fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F20444738&h=fc74f2e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180709/20444738</a></div>"},{"pid":"64af1e7aed2af13a2f097e62f55f7a741396483d","tid":734867,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"港大科斯產權研究中心聯同關注基層住屋聯席，去年11月及今年6月以問卷調查劏房住戶被濫收水電費情況，完成171份問卷。中心博士研究生梁嘉敏指91.8%住戶稱被多收電費，每度電收費平均為1.6元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，較中電平均淨電價每度電1.154元高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以4人家庭平均每月用電量400度計算，一般收461.6元，劏房戶需交640元，為一般的1.4倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。另外157戶有提供水費資料，逾九成住戶稱被多收水費，平均水費為每平方米13.4元，以4人家庭每月平均用水量13.65立方米計，水務署每平方米收約6元，即劏房水費是一般的2.2倍。<br />\n<br />\n港大房地產及建設系副主任蔡鴻達認為濫收水電情況嚴重，多收費用約佔租金5%，曾有住戶欲入稟追討，惟因欠缺租約等難以成功，批評政府拒規管劏房是失職。立法會議員邵家臻指據他了解兩電有計劃替住戶安裝獨立電錶，但過去2年中電只安裝了13戶，港燈的安裝數字更是零，令人失望。"},{"pid":"f7888f618ad407598b42463b1632a6f33ceb8f02","tid":734867,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"陳太與丈夫和兒子居於土瓜灣150呎劏房，月租5,000元，每月水電費達400多元，其租約列明的水電費水平均較一般高，但她因擔心被逼遷敢怒不敢言。李先生（化名）一家四口居於葵涌百多呎劏房，月租5,500元，水電費達1,000元，其租約列明每度電收1.5元，水費每立方米15元，他指「個個業主都咁樣收費，冇得反對，一係就唔住。」為慳電他晚上只開數小時冷氣，兒子「熱到生熱痱」，但無力追討多收費用。"},{"pid":"0bbb94492cd79adc1edda6dd0f96f4c9807a9975","tid":734867,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"400蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇開冷氣嘅月份先50蚊一個月"},{"pid":"8656091171aab769d407abc7de00f6809e23a7de","tid":734867,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcda3eea88307ef8256a84408ddea79fdce8ab81","tid":734867,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"業主個個都吸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3fac69423c53025c3dab8c07705ef92e52dd0a","tid":734867,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"算唔算轉售水電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04d126e8fa2f71125cd23e8d7996c88cad477dd","tid":734867,"uid":20025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"快d監管！d仆街業主呢小小錢都貪，祝佢地死全家"},{"pid":"c5643015665adb0860c74f63b6ac878ef9f11e8c","tid":734867,"uid":20025,"like":1,